        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 15 at 12:47AM MDT until June 15 at 1:15AM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 1245 AM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 9 miles northwest
of Sand Springs, or 34 miles west of Jordan, moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Sand Springs.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

Torrential rainfall is occurring with this storm which may lead to
ponding on area roadways.</instruction>
